data.description: Check out this barely lived in 2022 Manufactured Home that sits on 3.63 acres and get 100% FINANCING with a rural development loan! One of the best floor plans we have seen with multiple family rooms. Spacious rooms and tons of storage are offered in every nook to this property. Neutral colors were used throughout. The Primary Bedroom is large with a top of the line Primary Bathroom and walk in closet! The kitchen is the heart of the home with a breakfast bar and opens up to your Living Room and Dining Room. The upscale design selections will for sure win you over. Run out your front door and explore your rolling acreage with wood surround. Bonus features are the RV covered parking and a fenced in area for the dogs! Check this one out fast if you are ready for serenity and country living that's just minutes out from Bossier.
